{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3f7797ca19cba27584f90825",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！",
        "text_hash": "30fa801112a0346d965b0edfe667b10e7349b4896e2c01cb796b297c2595c5fc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a6e4ddaddd97af3e629f3f9e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪躲在沙发下面。",
        "text_hash": "20b2d5beb82ccf3229bc0a9ac4d9f4490b74f8293e2e152b066c7deb4a6aeb76",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d40893879afe476eeec20d74",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！和我一起玩。",
        "text_hash": "b9e8fa1d11c8dd815f0e2e263bd5a74a18cfc18f372426d92ebe267774390166",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee485ca1bff20432fbdab4d4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪跳起来，挂在窗帘上。",
        "text_hash": "00b5261c2ad44e29ee23c0b1e24870700c0d4d4349477b60f14cfb3cae31028f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1d310e83b15fa1d0fd4d0b7f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "坐到你的篮子里。待在这里别动！",
        "text_hash": "268b07f3307a1c6cbacfe54727cbbfa07bc8b8fd678901ec605e9bef773bc2e1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e718cc1354c1b2e0798c4ea7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪坐在她的篮子里。她很不高兴。",
        "text_hash": "e530365e6d9332bbbbfe0642588c87659c8d7920f1c7786034b4e234c02273ce",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ad0a4c27ca1058b13ab87512",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！那太高了。",
        "text_hash": "73aff03525c74c2b5c8c32d8f4bfbdc0b72c884dbf75ee7b2490e8fce73a346a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_87778ccff91ed7b66b5fdff5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪偷偷从后门溜了出去。",
        "text_hash": "3ce1122adf0448be778334f7a483e6d4715fb3f1b661a0c994f14e5a3d4b4519",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c20d5ff0f290cfcafa21ebc5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！别到外面去。",
        "text_hash": "8636840c1f249c4ae8d5171ae2322802e27b6891478cff9f16e79f38fb218919",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_583f0cace37fb8a6a5bb5795",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪跑到外面，追赶蝴蝶。",
        "text_hash": "106582542c5237634f41597bb81908841b8437dbcf24fd86c51f65842618f6c9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1ae47339842240752d84a5f8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪从晾衣绳上扯下一只袜子，把线拆开了。",
        "text_hash": "dafd90b33b75e5a42a7cf612c4a9cb8c8dd9f9ea1b9470998a7c1161903a7d4d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9f38fdc5f1b0c2cd5a5c6456",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！那不是你的。",
        "text_hash": "2aaf7b6c9c6e05a66a0a1fb8d1b4daf5fa0efc35f98323c25a21908ad1d3f219",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bebf1ea892061a5fe76b7fd4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪在泥土里发现了一只蜗牛。袜子上的线缠在了她的尾巴上。",
        "text_hash": "99ee7dccbfc17ba1761a95fa2b7dd114402ee6776a7fc2285863e111d857fdfd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_64b88b4dd00f112383788173",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪！你拿到了什么？",
        "text_hash": "b87f07cae62e455a203f3980e85972df4e9f999987c409b1ddcd336a0301713f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fa3c05adc446cbcfe31eeb80",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪遇到了一只鸡。现在猫咪尾巴上缠着线，背上还有那只蜗牛。",
        "text_hash": "149b20bab4a8f5b0395ab7b811126881a807443fbc46c0f02c417751ed87a30e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_85f73c874fa4fcf87918875e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回来，猫咪。",
        "text_hash": "fe1b96f8e166f748518ff86feef980a334d7eeb293eadecf750be787d829625a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_65b8d107aaefd9d047342ea8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "那不是你的朋友！",
        "text_hash": "bcdce81229ca0e393f656b652205c3ad4e913b5322be4c98e35d55b2d56e346c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a84d435cdfac41ad7fa45627",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "鸡毛在猫咪头边飘来飘去。她的尾巴上仍然缠着线，背上仍然背着那只蜗牛。",
        "text_hash": "2093708ef9add5fb504261b7ae13de46a6f5ae17212bfdb8150abf7c80c7889f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cb858a7a804b58e9e7e929ca",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "你好，猫咪！你回来了吗？",
        "text_hash": "198e48ef3baf137b40a7dc8ec02d844d03de132ca8b12b2314959a0b40218052",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f9ad0bdfc95a2fd3e5d0f552",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪躺在她的篮子里，看起来很满足。",
        "text_hash": "4571edea425f1eab8d90337d7af968a2b701a4c454b1206ed2904d17562207b4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_20f2dcb5bec5c55d77a0fa28",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "待在你的篮子里。现在是午睡时间。",
        "text_hash": "892f47a7b452f77ebfa2cec25aaba7ba8e06374ec4f3180ccfac5033f7c9312b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_86b8d54bf470339025308a43",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪的篮子空了，只剩下几根羽毛。",
        "text_hash": "f4881786f2421d46c3008098d1ed4269e6861feffcd12673ccc0cc5b447efe7e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9daff3aca925ddec86f0465f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪？",
        "text_hash": "b998e4f05589a34b5c366102177722b8ec5088079b0f928d3104ed5ef2073fb7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7dde3fdf3ea2a4de2529ee1a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猫咪带着羽毛、线和蜗牛，在沙发上安静地睡着了。",
        "text_hash": "62fefa114d638c1d4b09c54c0191b4ac4e4bddfa08af4b803fb4de30e9879d4b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_a169bab74cf7f655f8a6fc04"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
